<item>
            <title>[FELIX-3186] Adapter services do not get their adapted services transparently replaced when an aspect is added to them.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3186</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A service consumer consumes an adapter service. The adapter service adapts a service provider.&lt;br/&gt;
An aspect is added to the service provider. This should not impact the service consumer.&lt;br/&gt;
Expected behavior is transparent replacement of the service the adapter adapts with the aspect service.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>mac-osx</environment>
